                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>When a creature's shadow is pulled free by Steal Shadow, it becomes a @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.pathfinder-bestiary.Actor.Shadow]{Shadow Spawn} under the command of the shadow that created it. This shadow spawn doesn't have Steal Shadow and is perpetually and incurably @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Clumsy]{Clumsy 2}. If the creature the shadow spawn was pulled from dies, the shadow spawn becomes a full-fledged, autonomous shadow. If the creature recovers from its @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Enfeebled]{Enfeeblement}, its shadow returns to it and the shadow spawn is extinguished.</p>"
                },
